    retries = retries.increment(
  File "/home/user/.local/lib/python3.9/site-packages/urllib3/util/retry.py", line 519, in increment
    raise MaxRetryError(_pool, url, reason) from reason  # type: ignore[arg-type]
urllib3.exceptions.MaxRetryError: HTTPSConnectionPool(host='<hostname>', port=<port>): Max retries exceeded with url: /api/v3/health (Caused by SSLError(SSLCertVerificationError(1, "[SSL: CERTIFICATE_VERIFY_FAILED] certificate verify failed: Hostname mismatch, certificate is not valid for '<hostname>'. (_ssl.c:1129)")))

## Reproduction Steps

```python
